The paper focuses on enhancing user experience on Stack Overflow, which is a platform for knowledge sharing in the programming domain. This falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also deals with sentiment analysis and representation, which could be categorised under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of emojis to augment comments could also be related to Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) as it involves user interaction and security of the platform.
